<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Database on PIGSTY</title><link>https://pigsty.io/docs/pgsql/dashboard/database/</link><description>Recent content in Database on PIGSTY</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en</language><atom:link href="https://pigsty.io/docs/pgsql/dashboard/database/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>PGSQL Database</title><link>https://pigsty.io/docs/pgsql/dashboard/database/pgsql-database/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://pigsty.io/docs/pgsql/dashboard/database/pgsql-database/</guid><description>&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Main dashboard for a single PGSQL database: &lt;a href="https://demo.pigsty.io/d/pgsql-database"&gt;Demo&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;PGSQL Database is the main dashboard for a single PostgreSQL database, providing comprehensive database-level metrics.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://demo.pigsty.io/d/pgsql-database"&gt;&lt;img src="https://pigsty.io/img/panel/pgsql-database.webp" alt="pgsql-database"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>PGCAT Database</title><link>https://pigsty.io/docs/pgsql/dashboard/database/pgcat-database/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://pigsty.io/docs/pgsql/dashboard/database/pgcat-database/</guid><description>&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Database info from database catalog: &lt;a href="https://demo.pigsty.io/d/pgcat-database"&gt;Demo&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;PGCAT Database shows database-level information retrieved directly from PostgreSQL system catalog.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://demo.pigsty.io/d/pgcat-database"&gt;&lt;img src="https://pigsty.io/img/panel/pgcat-database.webp" alt="pgcat-database"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>PGSQL Tables</title><link>https://pigsty.io/docs/pgsql/dashboard/database/pgsql-tables/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://pigsty.io/docs/pgsql/dashboard/database/pgsql-tables/</guid><description>&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Table/index access metrics: &lt;a href="https://demo.pigsty.io/d/pgsql-tables"&gt;Demo&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;PGSQL Tables shows table and index access metrics for all objects within a single PostgreSQL database.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://demo.pigsty.io/d/pgsql-tables"&gt;&lt;img src="https://pigsty.io/img/panel/pgsql-tables.webp" alt="pgsql-tables"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>PGSQL Table</title><link>https://pigsty.io/docs/pgsql/dashboard/database/pgsql-table/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://pigsty.io/docs/pgsql/dashboard/database/pgsql-table/</guid><description>&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Detailed info for a single table: &lt;a href="https://demo.pigsty.io/d/pgsql-table"&gt;Demo&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;PGSQL Table shows detailed metrics for a single table including QPS, response time, index usage, and sequence info.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://demo.pigsty.io/d/pgsql-table"&gt;&lt;img src="https://pigsty.io/img/panel/pgsql-table.webp" alt="pgsql-table"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>PGCAT Table</title><link>https://pigsty.io/docs/pgsql/dashboard/database/pgcat-table/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://pigsty.io/docs/pgsql/dashboard/database/pgcat-table/</guid><description>&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Detailed table info from catalog: &lt;a href="https://demo.pigsty.io/d/pgcat-table"&gt;Demo&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;PGCAT Table shows detailed table information from database catalog including statistics and bloat analysis.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://demo.pigsty.io/d/pgcat-table"&gt;&lt;img src="https://pigsty.io/img/panel/pgcat-table.webp" alt="pgcat-table"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>PGSQL Query</title><link>https://pigsty.io/docs/pgsql/dashboard/database/pgsql-query/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://pigsty.io/docs/pgsql/dashboard/database/pgsql-query/</guid><description>&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Detailed info for a query type: &lt;a href="https://demo.pigsty.io/d/pgsql-query"&gt;Demo&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;PGSQL Query shows detailed metrics for a specific query type including QPS and response time distribution.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://demo.pigsty.io/d/pgsql-query"&gt;&lt;img src="https://pigsty.io/img/panel/pgsql-query.webp" alt="pgsql-query"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>PGCAT Query</title><link>https://pigsty.io/docs/pgsql/dashboard/database/pgcat-query/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://pigsty.io/docs/pgsql/dashboard/database/pgcat-query/</guid><description>&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Query details from database catalog: &lt;a href="https://demo.pigsty.io/d/pgcat-query"&gt;Demo&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;PGCAT Query shows query details from database catalog including SQL text and execution statistics.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://demo.pigsty.io/d/pgcat-query"&gt;&lt;img src="https://pigsty.io/img/panel/pgcat-query.webp" alt="pgcat-query"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>PGCAT Locks</title><link>https://pigsty.io/docs/pgsql/dashboard/database/pgcat-locks/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://pigsty.io/docs/pgsql/dashboard/database/pgcat-locks/</guid><description>&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Activity and lock wait info: &lt;a href="https://demo.pigsty.io/d/pgcat-locks"&gt;Demo&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;PGCAT Locks shows active sessions and lock wait information from database catalog.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://demo.pigsty.io/d/pgcat-locks"&gt;&lt;img src="https://pigsty.io/img/panel/pgcat-locks.webp" alt="pgcat-locks"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>PGCAT Schema</title><link>https://pigsty.io/docs/pgsql/dashboard/database/pgcat-schema/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://pigsty.io/docs/pgsql/dashboard/database/pgcat-schema/</guid><description>&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Schema info from database catalog: &lt;a href="https://demo.pigsty.io/d/pgcat-schema"&gt;Demo&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;PGCAT Schema shows schema-level information from database catalog including tables, indexes, and sequences.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://demo.pigsty.io/d/pgcat-schema"&gt;&lt;img src="https://pigsty.io/img/panel/pgcat-schema.webp" alt="pgcat-schema"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>